73
00:10:27,767 --> 00:10:28,766
Tudo bem.

74
00:10:28,768 --> 00:10:30,567
Suba e se arrume.

75
00:10:30,569 --> 00:10:33,204
Querem te ver
de novo de manhã.

76
00:10:34,059 --> 00:10:35,558
Obrigado, mãe.

77
00:10:41,480 --> 00:10:43,060
"Obrigado, mãe"?

78
00:10:43,482 --> 00:10:45,148
