pensar acordado à noite.

437
00:30:30,862 --> 00:30:32,133
Gower.

438
00:30:32,135 --> 00:30:34,568
Bom dia.
Grant MacLaren, FBI.

439
00:30:34,570 --> 00:30:37,138
